title: List of Valencia CF seasons
text:
This is a list of seasons played by <a href="Valencia%20CF">Valencia CF</a> in Spanish and European <a href="association%20football">football</a>, from 1919 to the most recent completed season. It details the club's achievements in major competitions, and the top scorers for each season.
The club has won the <a href="La%20Liga">Liga</a> six times, the <a href="Copa%20del%20Rey">Spanish Cup</a> eight times, the <a href="Supercopa%20de%20Espa%C3%B1a">Spanish Super Cup</a> one time, the <a href="Copa%20Eva%20Duarte">Copa Eva Duarte</a> one time, the <a href="UEFA%20Cup">UEFA Cup</a> three times, the <a href="UEFA%20Cup%20Winners%27%20Cup">European Cup Winners' Cup</a> one time, the <a href="UEFA%20Super%20Cup">European Super Cup</a> twice and the <a href="UEFA%20Intertoto%20Cup">Intertoto Cup</a> one time but has never won the <a href="UEFA%20Champions%20League">UEFA Champions League</a>, finishing runners-up twice.
